---
title: Chickpea and Plant-Based Ground Protein Shakshuka with Sesame Flatbreads and Feta
description: This dish – a breakfast staple in North Africa and parts of the Middle East – relies on tomatoes, peppers, eggs and a whole slew of spices. We've added chickpeas and plant-based ground protein to this version for extra nutrition. Make sure you mop up every morsel with the nutty sesame flatbread!
